                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/745.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consul
                        General <persName type="to">Hanna</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 5, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your August 4, 1 p.m. Department telegraphing Silliman endeavor obtain immediate
                    sending of desired instructions to tax collector, Monterey.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
